description:

Worn only once indoors for a photo-shoot. In mint condition. 
Soft leather and uber comfortable. 

Looks brilliant worn with jeans, wide-leg pants and summer dresses. 

Size: US 8. Fits true to size.

Overview:
* Super chunky platform from Jeffrey Campbell with metal trim
* Rich leather upper; ankle strap with an antiqued metal buckle
* Carved wooden heel; rubber
* 5" heel
* 2" platform
